        "welcome": "Welcome to the Vite template.",
        "hero": {
          "title": "Wraps & Coffee",
          "slogan": "We offer fresh salads, tasty wraps, baguettes and a varied selection of drinks.",
          "description": "Quality ingredients, prepared fresh every day in a cozy spot to slow down, meet friends or grab something good on the go.",
          "cta": "See the menu",
          "ctaPickup": "Order and pick up yourself",
          "upcomingEvent": "Upcoming event"
        },
        "menu": {
          "title": "Good food that fills you up",
          "summary": "You'll find fresh and satisfying salads loaded with crisp greens and your choice of topping such as shrimp salad, tuna salad or classic Caesar salad. Wraps provide another option for those looking to dine on the go; filled with rice and veggies, wraps feature various choices including chicken and feta, tandoori chicken, and vegetarian selections. Additionally, there are tasty baguettes like the chicken one with garlic, tomato and cucumber or mozzarella baguette that are perfect for a fulfilling meal.\n\nMoreover, if you're craving something heartier but still want to maintain your dietary choices, nachos served with rice, cheese, vegetables, and an assortment of meat-flavored options can be shared among friends – they make for hearty portions without feeling overly heavy.\n\nAll these meals offer balanced nutrition while being delicious, making it easy to leave the café satisfied yet healthy. The cafe menu ensures that there's something suitable for everyone's preference or dietary needs, maintaining a balance between taste and health consciousness.",
